name: Kawalan
description:
'Kawalan'(nothingness) is the term used by the creator to define the word 'Space'. He started exploring the space since 1997. We literally see a space as if it is empty or nothing's in there. But for sure, that not the reality of the creator. 

Some strip may lookalike but in every space, creator guaranteed that there will be no totally identical strips/pieces.
